-- Medicality Valencia - International Medical Centre
('Medicality Valencia', 'Medical Clinics', 'International Medical Centre in the heart of Valencia specializing in care for foreign patients and expats. Multinational team of highly qualified doctors with experience in different countries who can assist patients in English, French, German, Italian, Russian, and Spanish. Offers a broad range of medical specializations including general medicine, internal medicine, tropical medicine, dermatology, orthopedics, neurology, ENT (oto-rhino-laryngology), osteopathy, and complementary medicine like homeopathy and acupuncture. Combines cutting-edge techniques with conventional and complementary treatments. Patient-centered approach with personalized healing plans addressing physical, social, mental, and emotional aspects. High standards of medical equipment, hygiene, and personal warmth ensuring care comparable to patients'' home countries. Accepts major international insurance providers including Allianz, Aegon, AXA, Vivaz, and Cigna International.', 'Calle Pintor Sorolla 19, 46002 Valencia', 'Valencia', 'Valencia', '+34 962 324 155', 'info@medicality.es', 'https://medicality.es/en/', true, true, true, false, NOW(), NOW());
